      <title>捷蓝航空预计成本上升，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/jetblue-shares-fall-after-projecting-higher-costs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷蓝航空 (JetBlue Airways Corp.) 股价下跌，原因是该公司预计 2025 年的成本高于预期。尽管遭遇挫折，但该航空公司报告的第四季度亏损低于预期。布鲁克·萨瑟兰 (Brooke Sutherland) 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/jetblue-shares-fall-after-projecting-higher-costs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 16:07:07 GMT</pubDate>
